            "cause": "EDUCATION",
            "description": "The SRNU aims at improving collaboration among employees of the French departments at different Dutch universities. In order to achieve this, it runs a website (www.romanisten.nl). I am the webmaster of this website. In addition, it organizes a yearly workshop on topics in French studies aimed at secondary school teachers, academics and anyone who is interested. I co-organized to of these workshops and provided IT-support for a third. It also tries to improve the position of French in the Dutch educational system. In order to do so, I am the SRNU-representative in the Visiegroep Frans."
        },
