            "role": "Member",
            "company": {
                "id": null,
                "name": "Visiegroep Frans",
                "logo": null,
                "url": null
            },
            "cause": "EDUCATION",
            "description": "The Visiegroep Frans aims to improve the position of the French language in Dutch educational system. It is a collaboration between Levende talen (Union of secondary school language teachers), VLoF (a body representing educators of secondary school teachers), Kenniscentrum Frankrijk-Nederland (KFN, a network of scientists, business leaders, translators and teachers with an interest in the French speaking World) and the SRNU (a body representing employees of French departments at universities in the Netherlands). We wrote different position papers, policy view points and held talks with the ministry of Education (OCW), Onderwijsraad, Ons Onderwijs 2032, and the group of French speaking ambassadors at the Hague. I was involved in the writing and editing of different documents that formulate the group's view on policy with respect to French in the Dutch educational system. Together with Alicia Montoya, I was the main person in charge of formulating group's view points."
        },
